ly are illustrated by analyzing simulated as well as two real\ndatasets. A new model testing technique is introduced to evaluate the\nperformance of the multivariate models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Dec 2019 18:15:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-17"}
