ties and\nthe magnetization of the impurity-bath system, both of which are accessible to\nexperiment. Another proposed application are impurities immersed in a\ntwo-dimensional weakly interacting Bose gas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2019 09:28:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Oct 2020 18:23:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-29"}
