-pressure gas targets,\nwhich are currently being employed for scaling isolated attosecond pulse\ngeneration to x-ray photon energies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2019 10:43:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-21"}
