ion involving a PKC pathway. Altogether, calcium entries are\nderegulated in Bcr-Abl-expressing cells and could represent an interesting\ntherapeutic target in combination with TKI.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2019 11:12:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-18"}
